  <brief_title>A Korean Post-Marketing Surveillance Study On Pergoveris® (Follitropin Alfa + Lutropin Alfa)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Korean Post-Marketing Surveillance Study On Pergoveris® (Follitropin Alfa + Lutropin Alfa)</official_title>
