  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective study will collect safety information from more than 600 patients treated
      with Pergoveris®.

      During the Post-Marketing Surveillance (PMS) period, data about the patient´s background,
      patient's medical history, Pergoveris® indication, prior infertility medication, Pergoveris®
      treatment status, concomitant drugs, all adverse events (regardless of the causal
      relationship to Pergoveris®) and efficacy (follicular growth and clinical pregnancy) will be
      collected for study purposes.

      The post marketing surveillance is based on all cases treated with Pergoveris®.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
